  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strategy & Planning:</strong> Develop and implement comprehensive sales and marketing plans to achieve business objectives.</li><li><strong>Market Analysis:</strong> Research industry trends, competitor activities, and consumer behavior to identify opportunities.</li><li><strong>Campaign Management:</strong> Plan, execute, and monitor marketing campaigns (digital, social media, advertising) to increase brand awareness.</li><li><strong>Sales Execution:</strong> Generate leads, manage key accounts, and meet/exceed sales quotas.</li><li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Coordinate with product, sales, and creative teams to ensure consistent brand messaging.</li><li><strong>Performance Tracking:</strong> Utilize CRM software (e.g., Salesforce, HubSpot) and analytics to analyze data and report on ROI, conversion rates, and KPIs.</li><li><strong>Budgeting:</strong> Manage marketing budgets and allocate resources for promotional activities. </li></ul>",
